TwitterWatch by Totally Honest

URL: http://github.com/totallyhonest/TwitterWatch/tree

Watch your Twitter Status for changes in followers
Hacked together in 10 minutes
Needs lots of work
Thats where you come in

Requires PHP with curl support and a Twitter account. 
Use cron or a wrapper of some kind to fire this puppy at intervals which meet your exacting needs.

